                <run bold='true'>Summary</run>
                <run>Æ&#10;</run>
                <run bold='true'>This category represents reported bullying allegations recorded across all U.S. schools in the CRDC 2021–2022 dataset.</run>
                <run>Æ&#10;&#10;</run>
